{{Merge to|Parthenogenesis|date=October 2018}}
'''Parthenote''' also known as '''parthenogenote''', is an organism produced through [[parthenogenesis]] from an unfertilized [[egg cell]]. The parthenote is incapable of developing beyond the early embryonic stages.<ref>{{Cite journal|title=parthenote|url=http://www.thefreedictionary.com/parthenote|journal=The Free Dictionary}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://en.oxforddictionaries.com/definition/parthenote|title=parthenote - definition of parthenote in English {{!}} Oxford Dictionaries|website=Oxford Dictionaries {{!}} English|access-date=2017-01-03}}</ref>

